Bango,s,service,provides,a,platform,for,automated,mobile,billing,and,analytics,The,Events,Notification,API,allows,users,to,find,out,real,time,information,about,payments,subscriptions,and,marketing,opt,ins,Events,are,related,to,objects,within,the,Bango,system,such,as,purchases,made,and,marketing,subscriptions,and,are,described,as,an,action,on,that,object,The,API,uses,HTTP,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML